perceptual model & bit allocation
perceptual model: masking
i. tonal/noise masks (see [4])
ii. temporal masking (see [1])
iii. spreading function (masking spreads to neighbouring bands) ([1],[4])
iv. addition of simultaneous masking ([1],[4])


bit allocation:
i. energy based (see [3])
ii. global information